McSherryLessIsBetter - Class in jcolibri.method.retrieve.NNretrieval.similarity.local.recommenders
This function returns the similarity of two numbers following the McSherry - Less is Better formulae sim(c.a,q.a)= (max(a) - c.a) / (max(a)-min(a)) min(a) and max(a) must be defined by the designer. q.a is not taken into account.
McSherryLessIsBetter(double, double) - Constructor for class jcolibri.method.retrieve.NNretrieval.similarity.local.recommenders.McSherryLessIsBetter
Constructor. max and min values are ignored for enum types.
McSherryMoreIsBetter - Class in jcolibri.method.retrieve.NNretrieval.similarity.local.recommenders
This function returns the similarity of two numbers following the McSherry - More is Better formulae sim(c.a,q.a)= 1 - ((max(a) - c.a) / (max(a)-min(a))) min(a) and max(a) must be defined by the designer. q.a is not taken into account.
McSherryMoreIsBetter(double, double) - Constructor for class jcolibri.method.retrieve.NNretrieval.similarity.local.recommenders.McSherryMoreIsBetter
Constructor. max and min values are ignored for enum types.
